<ol>
<li><p> Determine the equilibrium solutions to <m>\displaystyle \frac{dy}{dx} = y^2 - y -2.</m>  
  Use the slope field shown in <xref ref="AutonomousSlopeField2026b"/> to confirm your finding.
</p>
<figure xml:id="AutonomousSlopeField2026b" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
