        <description>    A slope field on a square grid showing short line segments that tilt downward to the right above the x‑axis and tilt upward to the right below the x‑axis. Near the horizontal line y = 2, the segments are nearly horizontal. The slopes become steeper as y moves away from 2 in either direction.
</description>
